answers.answer: Wow, he's a big boy! My daughter was born at 39 weeks and 5 days, she was 7 lbs 13 oz and 20 inches long. Definitely a good thing you got him out when you did. :) congrats!

question: After 14hrs of labor my son Wyatt made his debut into the world!! Due to preeclampsia, we were induced at 37w+3...he is grunty they say so he has been in the special nursery since last night. Just glad he is here and that I am feeling better!! Oh and he was 7lbs 10ozs. 21 1/4 inches long..Lol He deff would have been a nine pound baby had we waited!
title: Baby Wyatt is HERE!!
